{"lastModified":1764348561661,"uri":"c::7819256862::vessel::d5cc2415-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Summer Operating Area: West Mediterranean - Riviera/Corsica/Sardinia, Spain/Balearics\nWinter Operating Area: U.S. Virgin Islands, British Virgin Islands\n\nYCM 120 is a 37m / 120ft Luxury Motor Superyacht built in 2006 by International Shipyard Ancona (ISA Yachts) with interior design by Cristiano Gatto Design, Luxury Projects and later underwent a refit in 2024. Sleeping 10 guests in 5 cabins and with a crew of 6. Cruising at 19.00 kn/ph with a top speed of 26.00 kn/ph. The guest cabins comprise a primary suite with a queen size bed and en-suite bathroom facilities, 2 cabins with a queen size bed and en-suite bathroom facilities and 2 cabins with a twin bed and en-suite bathroom facilities.","blueprint":{"name":"YCM 120","images":["/media/media::image::c::7819256862::vessel::d5cc2415-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::3ff0bc90-7472-11ef-bfca-056e0a0804a0/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7819256862::vessel::d5cc2415-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::6f839c90-da4c-11ee-b993-0b3fde7b0598.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7819256862::vessel::d5cc2415-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::6f83eab0-da4c-11ee-b993-0b3fde7b0598.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7819256862::vessel::d5cc2415-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::6f83c3a0-da4c-11ee-b993-0b3fde7b0598.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7819256862::vessel::d5cc2415-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::3fea53f0-7472-11ef-bfca-056e0a0804a0/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7819256862::vessel::d5cc2415-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::3feb3e51-7472-11ef-bfca-056e0a0804a0/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7819256862::vessel::d5cc2415-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::3feb3e50-7472-11ef-bfca-056e0a0804a0/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7819256862::vessel::d5cc2415-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::6f15ad00